text: Md.Nurul Islam is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jamalpur-4. ==Career== Islam was elected to parliament from Jamalpur-4 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1996. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:6th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md.Nurul Islam
